h3 Intro

p.
  The main functionality this plugin provides is the side menu handling for
  mobile devices. It binds to the <em>burger</em> icon and triggers the
  toggling of the menu.

h3 Usage

p Activate the functionality with the data-* API

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      <a data-toggle="site-menu" data-target=".site" ></a>

p Activate the functionality with JavaScript:

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      $('body.site').site(options)

