h4 Methods

h5: code .site('toggleMenu')

p Manually toggles the menu.

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      $('body.site').site('toggleMenu')

h5: code .site('showMenu')

p Manually shows the menu. Doesn't do anything when the menu is already open.

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      $('body.site').site('showMenu')

h5: code .site('hideMenu')

p Manually hides the menu. Doesn't do anything when the menu is already hidden.

.highlight
  pre.highlight__listing.hljs: code.js
    :highlight
      $('body.site').site('hideMenu')

